                            Our website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small text files stored on your device that help us understand how you use our site. You can manage cookie preferences through our <a href="/cookie" class="text-warning">Cookie Policy</a> page.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section class="mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 mb-3" style="color: #d4af37;">
                            <i class="fas fa-lock me-2"></i>Data Security
                        </h2>
